fit                     Optimization wrapper, maximizing the joint
                        model of total (TReC) and allele specific (ASE)
                        counts for autosomes
fitsh                   Optimization wrapper, maximizing the joint
                        model of total (TReC) and allele specific (ASE)
                        counts for autosomes
makeXmatr               Create example design matrix for simulations
readCounts              A list object that should be used as input to
                        optimization fit or fitsh function.
simu2                   Simulate a dataset in a format acceptable by a
                        fit function
simu4                   Simulate a dataset in a format acceptable by a
                        fit function
